latestPosts.caption:
battle of the pro’s 💖

@patricktabeauty blush duo in she’s a barbie doll 
@makeupbymario blush veil in pink paradise

I personally prefer the makeup by mario one especially when it comes to this popping shade of pink, both are very pigmented and can easily go overboard. I felt like blush veil is more dewy compared to patrick ta which is a bit thicker formula…therefore its more easy to blend, especially if you’re a beginner 💖

the shades are identical, and patrick ta has powder in it as well which is a bonus 🫶🏼

the shade NN03 ginger was a bit light on me, otherwise the product is worth the hype 🤎
